00:28:11.490 --> 00:28:12.900
Babbage has an
addressing system.

00:28:12.900 --> 00:28:16.170
The machine is an incredibly
beautiful and incredibly clever

00:28:16.170 --> 00:28:19.530
thing, and really
shockingly like a computer.

00:28:19.530 --> 00:28:21.540
This is the store.

00:28:21.540 --> 00:28:22.390
This is short.

00:28:22.390 --> 00:28:25.160
The store would have gone
