00:32:16.910 --> 00:32:18.784
Now you understand how
everything's going on.

00:32:23.310 --> 00:32:24.799
It runs in cycles
like a computer.

00:32:24.799 --> 00:32:26.215
They're just way,
way, way slower.

00:32:30.290 --> 00:32:32.630
Multiplication might
