00:32:46.040 --> 00:32:48.820
incredibly detailed.

00:32:48.820 --> 00:32:51.030
This is not an abstract concept.

00:32:51.030 --> 00:32:54.030
Babbage left extremely detailed
plans for all these levers.

00:32:54.030 --> 00:32:57.980
He thought through all the
timing, all the weights

00:32:57.980 --> 00:32:59.470
