00:42:37.910 --> 00:42:40.640
I mean, it's just a
completely extraordinary feat

00:42:40.640 --> 00:42:42.530
of imagination to see
that in the machine.

00:42:46.904 --> 00:42:48.820
I'm just completely blown
away by their genius

00:42:48.820 --> 00:42:51.940
and I'm humbled by it.

00:42:51.940 --> 00:42:53.190
